transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Ji madam.
Executive: Ji sir, namaste. Mai Shruti baat kar rahi hu IndiaMART head office se.
Customer: Bolie na.
Executive: Sir actually mujhe thoda sa na subscription ke regarding baat karni thi. Aapki na Tanuj ke saath baat hui hogi aapke account.
Customer: Madam ne wo 3 baje ka time diya tha aapko kal.
Executive: Ya I know sir but actually ek meeting ho gayi thi to thoda miss ho gaya tha. Fir mujhe laga ki aap available honge nahi honge isliye fir main abhi nahi hu 5:30 baje.
Customer: Achcha to usi time pe available rahenge?
Executive: 3 baje kijiye na humko.
Executive: Ji.
summary:
